FBIS4-34493 "drlat119_b_94002" FBIS-LAT-94-119 Daily Report 20 Jun 1994 Barbados Alternative Party Leader Offers `Better Way' Alternative Party Leader Offers `Better Way' FL2106014094 Castries HTS Caribvision Television in English 1945 GMT 20 Jun 94 FL2106014094 Castries HTS Caribvision Television English BFN [Text] National Democratic Party leader Dr. Richie Haynes says that his party too is ready to offer Barbadians an alternative to the two main political parties. [Begin Haynes recording] The National Democratic Party gave Barbadians the opportunity once again to make a clean break with the confusion, the corruption, the abuse of authority, the neglect of the people, the victimization, the arrogance, and the incompetence which have characterized both recent Democratic Labor Party and Barbados Labor Party administrations and offers them a better way and a new path for this beloved country of ours. [end recording]
